onboarding-live-status-listening-title = Listening for a dragged-in PDF
onboarding-live-status-pdf-detected-body = Zotero may still be retrieving metadata, and auto scan also waits until the PDF attachment is ready before queueing. Keep this window open and wait a few seconds.
onboarding-live-status-listening-body = After you drag a PDF into the middle items area, the status here updates automatically. If Zotero is fetching the title, authors, or DOI, the tutorial will wait here.
